text: When the platform is running and you are logged in, you gain access to a more extensive set of commands for system management. These commands are: change-password configuration derbybackup desktop desktopadmin disconnect dumpsyslog generate_pcc_classes importrollback logger packageexport pico plist premove refreshdbmeta resumeexecution service sldreg slowmethods systemexport systemimport trace ultra unregister user vcexport vcimport wfcommand wfdebug wfexport wfdisable wfenable wflist wfgroupdisable wfgroupenable wfgroupaddwf wfgroupaddwfgroup wfgrouplist wfgroupmodify wfgroupremovewf wfgroupremovewfgroup wfgroupstart wfgroupstop wfimport wfstart wfstop
